nl.bioinf.lscheffer_wvanhelvoirt.insanemodel.model

Class Membrane

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.bioinf.lscheffer_wvanhelvoirt.insanemodel.model.Membrane

  • public class Membrane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the membrane and all membrane related parameters that can be set in insane.py. It contains arrays of standard lipids and additional lipids, and validates the parameters that might cause an exception in insane.

        Parameters:
        errorMessages - the list to add error messages to
        standardLipids - the array of standard lipids
        additionalLipids - the array of additional lipids
        grid - the grid for this simulation
        randomKick - the random kick
        areaLowerLipids - the ratio of lipids in the lower membrane leaflet
        areaUpperLipids - the ratio of lipids in the upper membrane leaflet
        membraneAsymmetry - the amount of asymmetric lipids in the membrane
        hole - the membrane hole size
        disc - the membrane disc size
        beadDistance - the distance between the membrane beads
